</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GivingTheSwordToANoob' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GivingTheSwordToANoob'>Giving the Sword to a Noob</a>  <br />A moron is trusted with a vital weapon or device, and tries to use it instead of giving it to the right person.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GladiatorGames' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GladiatorGames'>Gladiator Games</a>  <br />Where people have to fight each other, or monsters, to the death while lots of people look on and cheer.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GladiatorRevolt' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GladiatorRevolt'>Gladiator Revolt</a>  <br />Where the hero, captured as a gladiator, starts a rebellion with the gladiators breaking out of the slave pits.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GogglesDoSomethingUnusual' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GogglesDoSomethingUnusual'>Goggles Do Something Unusual</a>  <br />Eyewear that does something other than what their mundane design purpose is.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GotVolunteered' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GotVolunteered'>Got Volunteered</a>  <br />When a character is dragooned into a dangerous job against their will.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GovernmentAgencyOfFiction' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GovernmentAgencyOfFiction'>Government Agency of Fiction</a>  <br />Either a fictional government agency, or a real one described in a fictional way.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GraveRobbing' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GraveRobbing'>Grave Robbing</a>  <br />Because dead bodies are always useful <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ForSCIENCE' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ForSCIENCE'>For SCIENCE</a>!
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GreatEscape' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GreatEscape'>Great Escape</a>  <br />Breaking out of prison.
</li><li> <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GrimyWater' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GrimyWater'>Grimy Water</a>  <br />&#8212;&gt;<em>Stop falling in the death water!</em>  <br />&#8212; <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LetsPlay' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LetsPlay'>Proton Jon</a>, <a class='urllink' href='http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BCjMWKSpvHI'>Let's Play Mario's Wacky World - World 2 Part 1<img src="http://static.mediatropes.info/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;" /></a>
